    "causal_summary": "The skill currently named `sk-improve-prompt` carries a redundant `-improve-` segment that duplicates intent already encoded by its dispatcher command (`/improve:prompt`) and agent (`@improve-prompt`). Sibling skills that surface a single capability use single-word names (`sk-code`, `sk-doc`, `sk-git`). Renaming to `sk-prompt` aligns with that convention while preserving the `sk-` family marker.",
